Package com.adobe.cq.projects.api

Defines top level Project interfaces.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Project
    Defines the interface for a CQ Project.
    ProjectLink
    Defines the interface for a CQ Project Link.
    ProjectManager
    The ProjectManager provides the ability to retrieve projects, delete projects, and create projects.
    ProjectMember
    Represents a member of a team.
    ProjectMemberRole
    The ProjectMemberRole represents the role a user has in a project team.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ProjectFilter
    used to filter projects in ProjectManager
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    ProjectException
    ProjectException provides a base Exception class for Projects.
